"text":"怎樣乘搭校車"},
{"image":"/images/story38_p1_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story38_p1_m.mp3",
"text":"校車通常會在特定的時間，接我上學"},
{"image":"/images/story38_p2_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story38_p2_m.mp3",
